{"TopicId":202616,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Complex medical care for Kerbals in space.","CreatedByName":"Earthbound Spartan","CreatedById":202301,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-23T15:13:27Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Earthbound Spartan","CreatedById":202301,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-23T15:13:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is an idea for a mod, I don\u0027t know if something similar has been posted before on this forum. I think it would be cool if a mod allowed complex medical care for the Kerbals, where analogs to human diseases related to space travel were used. For example, effects of microgravity, radiation, injuries from falls, explosions, blows, etc., that influence kerbal parameters such as its speed of translation, jump, as well as its precision in \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E mode, not to mention the loss of life or the full ability to do anything. It could be related to other life support mods (like Kerbalism or TACLS), causing diseases derived from the lack of O2, food, water, CO2 poisoning, and so on. The mod could include medical specialists, medical bay modules, medical supplies (and \u003Cabbr title=\u0022In-Situ Resource Utilization\u0022\u003EISRU\u003C/abbr\u003E for it), etc., especially for small planetary colonies and interplanetary / interstellar vehicles. What do you think about this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-24T13:23:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt was mentioned in the Suggestions section for stock a few weeks back and was welcomed on the whole although not as in as much detail as you\u2019ve listed. I like the idea as long as it\u2019s not TOO micromanagementy although many players do enjoy that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sebi.zzr","CreatedById":81294,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-25T14:12:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022141813\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed6212915168\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/155313-18-kerbal-health-153-2021-04-12/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:195px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-25T15:09:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd dentists.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Earthbound Spartan","CreatedById":202301,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-05-25T18:03:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223978512\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022202616\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221621951932\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002281294\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sebi.zzr\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, sebi.zzr said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022141813\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed3066244512\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/155313-18-kerbal-health-153-2021-04-12/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:197px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks a lot...\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p